data.description: This property is characterized by its well-maintained, sizable split level style home along with the tranquil, private, park-like land that it sits on. Set in a sought after area, this home will surely captivate your heart and help create a vision for what you and your family can grow into. The house is open and warm and offers 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths. Through the front door, you will be invited into the living room with its picture window and where pride in ownership will be noticed that will be evident throughout the entire home. Connected to the living room is the formal dining room that feels so inviting. The kitchen is charming and has a pantry, stainless steel appliances and corian countertops and a perfect area for seating. There is a screened-in sunroom that is so ideal. It connects to the exterior of the home where there is a truly spectacular outdoor oasis, marked with wooden decking and an inground pool making the entire property truly ideal for enjoying quiet time or hosting family and friends throughout the seasons and for holidays. The remainder of the home has 3 bedrooms on the top floor, a full bath and closets for linens. Complementing the home and on the lowest level, is a comfy sitting room with a wood burning fireplace. The space is well designed and equipped with a bar, an office area, a half bath, a laundry room and access to both the garage and the backyard. The space, with its own entrance, can also be used as an artist studio, seperate living space and/or a totally dedicated office. The home is about 1 hour from NYC. Also within minutes, appreciate easy access to 684, the Metro North Train and Route 6. Within close proximity are shopping, restaurants and parks like Mahopac Lake. Enjoy a home that you can truly be proud of and that has been cared for with pride inside and out. This is a beautiful property!
